name: Rubber Ducky Go Fish (Demo)
description:
Rubber Ducky Go Fish is an endless, collectible item fishing game. Sail around the lake on a giant inflatable rubber duck and cast your rod to catch a variety of fish!

You start off with your trusty ol’ fishing rod. Each time you manage to hook a fish, you will enter into a randomized short mini-game where you have to use your wits, luck, and skill to win to successfully earn your catch!

Note: This is a demo version
